(STATIC)

34:09.923 --> 34:11.333
Fargo!

34:21.476 --> 34:23.012
Dr. Thatcher.

34:38.660 --> 34:39.991
I got that.

34:46.084 --> 34:49.747
He's been carrying
that speech for 40 years.

