more powerful,
more deadly weapons,

35:42.641 --> 35:46.429
which is what led me
to my greatest achievement,

35:47.437 --> 35:50.304
the lonosphere Particle Beam.

35:51.274 --> 35:55.142
In order to ensure
peace on earth,

35:56.154 --> 36:01.023
