of the story.

36:06.665 --> 36:08.530
Let me take you back
to the beginning.

36:09.000 --> 36:10.581
We don't have time
to go back to Never Land.

36:11.628 --> 36:13.493
Dr. Thatcher,
there's an urgent situation

36:13.546 --> 36:15.673
that needs your attention.

36:15.799 --> 36:17.255
Oh.
Sorry.

36:18.677 --> 36:23.091
I would just like to end
by thanking the committee.

36:24.766 --> 36:27.473
And Eugenia, my love,

36:28.353 --> 36:32.437
without whom this achievement
would not have been possible.

36:35.276 --> 36:37.688
