of catching up to do.

36:45.286 --> 36:47.026
I don't like that look.
What's wrong?

36:47.122 --> 36:51.081
My crew. I've got to get
my crew to fix the device.

36:51.167 --> 36:53.544
You have a crew?

36:56.506 --> 36:59.543
(EVE OF DESTRUCTION PLAYING)

37:24.409 --> 37:26.695
Oh, for the love of God.

37:28.204 --> 37:29.819
Thirty seconds
and counting, guys.

37:30.081 --> 37:32.072
(ALL GASPING)

37:44.471 --> 37:47.178
Ready, set,

37:48.516 --> 37:52.304
go! Key one, two and off.

38:14.125 --> 38:16.616
