Launch code
override initiated.

38:18.129 --> 38:19.118
Yes!

38:19.380 --> 38:21.632
(EVE OF DESTRUCTION RESUMING)

38:24.511 --> 38:25.500
All right!

38:32.560 --> 38:34.767
(ALL EXCLAIMING)

38:39.108 --> 38:41.064
(RUMBLING)

38:49.702 --> 38:50.691
Oh, crap.

38:50.787 --> 38:52.493
ELECTRONIC VOICE:
Dead man's protocol activated.

