Launch sequence initiated.

38:54.290 --> 38:57.453
Second strike weapon
will deploy in ﬁve minutes.

39:01.339 --> 39:04.831
Did somebody cut
the blue wire?

39:11.015 --> 39:12.755
Not good.

39:12.851 --> 39:14.136
Very not good.

39:15.103 --> 39:19.267
This is the one that assures
mutually assured destruction.

39:19.357 --> 39:20.767
How do we stop it?

39:20.859 --> 39:24.192
I can't.
It can't be shut down.

39:25.238 --> 39:26.318
Henry, how much time
do we have left?

39:26.364 --> 39:27.353
Thirty seconds.

39:32.453 --> 39:34.865
CARTER:
Is there any way
we can re-aim it?

39:34.956 --> 39:38.869
Once it's locked on
to its target,
it can't be realigned.

39:43.214 --> 39:44.374
Will it work?

39:44.465 --> 39:46.797
I think desperate times
call for desperate measures.

39:46.885 --> 39:49.422
Henry, when you
outfitted my Jeep,
did you put in any airbags?

39:50.722 --> 39:55.011
ELECTRONIC VOICE:
...six, ﬁve, four...
Carter, are you crazy?

39:56.144 --> 40:00.808
...three, two, one.

40:03.568 --> 40:05.524
Henry, you got it?
I got it.

40:11.242 --> 40:14.075
lt missed!
We missed the moon!

40:17.415 --> 40:18.916
HENRY: Carter! Carter!

40:19.000 --> 40:20.615
Greatjob, man.
We missed the moon!

40:20.710 --> 40:23.167
We missed the moon!
We missed it!

40:25.089 --> 40:26.374
Little help.

40:27.800 --> 40:29.415
But where did it go?

40:32.138 --> 40:34.925
MAN: The Zephyr Rover
